    "Synthesis and Analysis: Table 6 summarizes CNNs key aspects, and the evolution of FL-based IDS models demonstrates a promising direction for securing IoT networks.",
    "But still, there is room for more improvement.",
    "Such as all models include their inability to completely address complex attacks such as model poisoning attacks, data poisoning attacks, and adversarial attacks in diverse networks.",
    "Additionally, FedACNN and SBA show promise in addressing the issues of data heterogeneity and optimal communication efficiency through dynamic weighting and client classification, but these solutions are not always scalable or resilient against multi-modal attacks.",
